OL,3,CPolice watchdog launches probe into
OL,4,Ccontact with paramedic before woman's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FThe police watchdog has announced an
OL,8,Finquiry into two forces' contact with
OL,9,Fparamedic Daniel Duffield in the weeks
OL,10,Fbefore the murder of student nurse
OL,11,FLauren Evans.
OL,13,FThe bodies of Duffield, who starred in
OL,14,FChannel 4's documentary series 999: On
OL,15,FThe Frontline, and Ms Evans were both
OL,16,Ffound at a house in Hednesford, near
OL,17,FCannock, Staffordshire, on June 25.
