OL,3,CPolice watchdog launches probe into
OL,4,Ccontact with paramedic before woman's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FIn a statement issued on Friday, the
OL,8,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,9,F(IOPC) said Staffordshire Police
OL,10,Fdetained Duffield under the Mental
OL,11,FHealth Act on May 10 and took him to a
OL,12,Fhospital.
OL,14,FThe watchdog also confirmed that South
OL,15,FWales Police had "face-to-face
OL,16,Fcontact" with 24-year-old Duffield on
OL,17,FMay 14 "when he came into the force
OL,18,Farea, over information received by
OL,19,Fpolice".
