OL,3,CPolice watchdog launches probe into
OL,4,Ccontact with paramedic before woman's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FThe IOPC said: "Following separate
OL,8,Freferrals from both forces at the end
OL,9,Fof last month, we have decided to
OL,10,Finvestigate contact police had with Mr
OL,11,FDuffield, in the weeks before his and
OL,12,FMs Evans' deaths.
OL,14,F"In particular, we will be focusing on
OL,15,Finteractions officers had with Mr
OL,16,FDuffield between 10 May and 14 May
OL,17,F2024."
