OL,3,CPolice watchdog launches probe into
OL,4,Ccontact with paramedic before woman's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FIOPC director David Ford said: "First
OL,8,Fand foremost, my thoughts and
OL,9,Fsympathies are with Lauren and
OL,10,FDaniel's families and friends at this
OL,11,Fvery difficult time.
OL,13,F"We are meeting with both families to
OL,14,Fexplain our role and how our
OL,15,Finvestigation will progress.
