OL,3,CPolice watchdog launches probe into
OL,4,Ccontact with paramedic before woman's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,F"We are independent of the police and
OL,8,Fit is important that we carry out a
OL,9,Fthorough investigation, to fully
OL,10,Festablish the circumstances of what
OL,11,Fhappened prior to the tragic events of
OL,12,F25 June. We will be examining concerns
OL,13,Ffor welfare reported to police about
OL,14,FLauren and Daniel, and whether
OL,15,Fappropriate action was taken by both
OL,16,Fforces."
