OL,3,CPolice watchdog launches probe into
OL,4,Ccontact with paramedic before woman's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FThe inquiry will consider if
OL,8,F"appropriate steps were taken to
OL,9,Fsafeguard the welfare of Ms Evans and
OL,10,FMr Duffield and whether police
OL,11,Fofficers and staff acted in accordance
OL,12,Fwith local and national policies and
OL,13,Fprocedures".
OL,15,FStaffordshire Police has said it is
OL,16,Ftreating the death of mental health
OL,17,Fnursing student Ms Evans, who was from
OL,18,FBridgend in South Wales, as a murder
OL,19,Fand has said no other party is being
OL,20,Fsought.
