OL,7,FIn a statement issued last week, her
OL,8,Ffamily said: "On 25 June 2024, we
OL,9,Ftragically, prematurely and
OL,10,Funnecessarily had our beautiful
OL,11,Fdaughter Lauren taken from us at the
OL,12,Ftender age of 22.
OL,14,F"Lauren was truly beautiful inside and
OL,15,Fout and will forever be in our
OL,16,Fmemories.
OL,26,@pD@NOUvD@AOU
